<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The king of mountain passes is the Lan-Evo!</b></font>

152
00:10:10,584 --> 00:10:13,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Darn! Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

153
00:10:13,184 --> 00:10:16,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't you mad at all after all that talk?!</b></font>

154
00:10:16,194 --> 00:10:18,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I was pretty angry.</b></font>

155
00:10:18,794 --> 00:10:21,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So why didn't you say anything?!</b></font>

156
00:10:21,564 --> 00:10:25,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Watching you get furious...</b></font>

157
00:10:25,034 --> 00:10:27,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...somehow calmed me down.</b></font>

158
00:10:27,434 --> 00:10:29,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck is up with that?</b></font>

159
00:10:29,774 --> 00:10:33,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Besides, there have been guys
who talked like that before, right?</b></font>

160
00:10:33,804 --> 00:10:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Right...
--Arguing with them doesn't do any good.</b></font>

161
00:10:37,484 --> 00:10:40,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't really tell who's faster
unless you actually race.</b></font>

162
00:10:40,914 --> 00:10:43,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see your point.</b></font>

163
00:10:43,414 --> 00:10:47,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I can't just stand there when
someone insults the Eight-Six like that!</b></font>

164
00:10:47,494 --> 00:10:50,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because I've always admired the Eight-Six.</b></font>

165
00:10:50,924 --> 00:10:53,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know the Eight-Six is an old model.</b></font>

166
00:10:53,624 --> 00:10:57,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's got no turbo, and it's slow on the uphill.</b></font>

167
00:10:58,064 --> 00:11:00,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But in the true fan's mind,</b></font>

168
00:11:00,164 --> 00:11:04,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the Eight-Six is faster than any other car!</b></font>

169
00:11:04,574 --> 00:11:07,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, stop crying. Here you go.</b></font>

170
00:11:07,044 --> 00:11:08,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

171
00:11:08,544 --> 00:11:10,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drink your coffee.</b></font>

172
00:11:10,914 --> 00:11:12,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks.</b></font>

173
00:11:15,584 --> 00:11:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi. You can do it, right?</b></font>

174
00:11:18,024 --> 00:11:20,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can beat the Lan-Evo on a downhill,</b></font>

175
00:11:20,224 --> 00:11:22,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and crush the ego of that
cocky long-haired guy!</b></font>

176
00:11:22,694 --> 00:11:27,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know. He said he
wouldn't race the Eight-Six.</b></font>

177
00:11:28,694 --> 00:11:31,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I've got it... The turbo!
--What?</b></font>

178
00:11:31,634 --> 00:11:35,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we added turbo to the Eight-Six,
it would be amazing, Takumi!</b></font>

179
00:11:53,124 --> 00:11:56,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This Lan-Evo jerk certainly sounds obnoxious.</b></font>

180
00:11:56,124 --> 00:11:58,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I was so furious!</b></font>

181
00:11:58,924 --> 00:12:03,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if they're the guys who
came to challenge Thunder Fire?</b></font>

182
00:12:03,064 --> 00:12:07,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're members of a team
called Emperor or something.</b></font>

183
00:12:07,004 --> 00:12:10,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard they're from Nikko
and they only drive Lan-Evos,</b></font>

184
00:12:10,844 --> 00:12:15,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and that they're extremely cocky,
but they drive very fast.</b></font>

185
00:12:15,414 --> 00:12:18,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard they beat Thunder Fire into the ground.</b></font>

186
00:12:18,444 --> 00:12:20,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard about that, too.</b></font>

187
00:12:20,884 --> 00:12:24,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They supposedly said that
they wanted to rule Gunma,</b></font>

188
00:12:24,084 --> 00:12:27,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so they might show up in Akina.</b></font>

189
00:12:27,084 --> 00:12:28,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you serious?!</b></font>

190
00:12:28,454 --> 00:12:30,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if they were checking
out the area yesterday?</b></font>

191
00:12:30,924 --> 00:12:33,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo will be really hard to beat...</b></font>

192
00:12:33,424 --> 00:12:36,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...even for Takumi's Eight-Six.</b></font>

193
00:12:36,464 --> 00:12:39,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

194
00:12:39,064 --> 00:12:41,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, putting these guys aside,</b></font>

195
00:12:41,474 --> 00:12:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we never know when or who
he'll be racing from now on.</b></font>

196
00:12:47,404 --> 00:12:49,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So because of that,</b></font>

197
00:12:49,044 --> 00:12:52,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we definitely need to beef up his Eight-Six.</b></font>

198
00:12:52,444 --> 00:12:54,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right?! Right?!</b></font>

199
00:12:54,314 --> 00:12:56,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what I'm talking about!</b></font>

200
00:12:56,654 --> 00:12:59,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Adding turbo to the Eight-Six.</b></font>

201
00:12:59,124 --> 00:13:00,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a good idea!</b></font>

202
00:13:00,484 --> 00:13:02,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, good for Itsuki.</b></font>

203
00:13:02,924 --> 00:13:08,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It might be easier for him to just
switch to a faster car, of course.</b></font>

204
00:13:08,694 --> 00:13:13,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I just can't imagine him driving
anything other than the Eight-Six.</b></font>

205
00:13:13,534 --> 00:13:17,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. We want him to stick to the Eight-Six.</b></font>

206
00:13:17,074 --> 00:13:18,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're both so right!</b></font>

207
00:13:18,504 --> 00:13:22,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The coolest part is that he drives
the Eight-Six and he's darn fast!</b></font>

208
00:13:22,614 --> 00:13:25,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, give it some thought.</b></font>

209
00:13:25,014 --> 00:13:27,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know...</b></font>

210
00:13:27,414 --> 00:13:30,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's my father's car, you know.</b></font>

211
00:13:30,054 --> 00:13:32,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right, I forgot...</b></font>

212
00:13:32,224 --> 00:13:36,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't we somehow convince your father?</b></font>

213
00:13:36,024 --> 00:13:39,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got it! If we told him
we'd pay for everything,</b></font>

214
00:13:39,424 --> 00:13:41,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet he wouldn't object!</b></font>

215
00:13:41,134 --> 00:13:45,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're right! I bet he'd love
having his car souped up!</b></font>

216
00:13:45,804 --> 00:13:48,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about it, Takumi?!</b></font>

217
00:13:48,304 --> 00:13:51,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the car were more powerful,
its fuel economy would suffer, right?</b></font>

218
00:13:51,944 --> 00:13:53,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, sort of.</b></font>

219
00:13:53,474 --> 00:13:55,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then we've got no chance.</b></font>

220
00:13:55,074 --> 00:13:57,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because my dad is stingy as hell.</b></font>

221
00:13:59,244 --> 00:14:02,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't say things like that
to spoil our image of him!</b></font>

222
00:14:02,154 --> 00:14:06,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your dad is our idol, you know!</b></font>

223
00:14:06,184 --> 00:14:11,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! That man is your idol?</b></font>

224
00:14:11,664 --> 00:14:13,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey...</b></font>

225
00:14:13,024 --> 00:14:15,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You shouldn't waste time
trying to convince him.</b></font>

226
00:14:15,894 --> 00:14:17,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We should just go ahead</b></font>

227
00:14:17,064 --> 00:14:20,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with the "Akina Eight-Six
Power-Up Project" ourselves!</b></font>

228
00:14:20,704 --> 00:14:22,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right! Let's do it!</b></font>

229
00:14:54,104 --> 00:14:55,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Long time no see, Ryosuke.</b></font>

230
00:14:55,974 --> 00:14:59,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi Sudo. I thought it was you.</b></font>

231
00:15:02,214 --> 00:15:04,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you up to?</b></font>

232
00:15:04,484 --> 00:15:06,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Easy, now! You should be nicer,</b></font>

233
00:15:06,744 --> 00:15:09,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>seeing as how we haven't
seen each other in over a year.</b></font>

234
00:15:09,684 --> 00:15:13,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're bored because we don't have
anyone to play with in our hood.</b></font>

235
00:15:13,384 --> 00:15:17,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So we came looking for some
high-spirited playmates, that's all.</b></font>

236
00:15:17,094 --> 00:15:20,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since this will be our playground,</b></font>

237
00:15:20,694 --> 00:15:24,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we thought we'd say hi
to the people here today.</b></font>

238
00:15:24,534 --> 00:15:27,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How considerate of you. Do as you wish.</b></font>

239
00:15:27,534 --> 00:15:30,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But here in Akagi,</b></font>

240
00:15:30,104 --> 00:15:33,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the playtime won't be as fun as you think...</b></font>

241
00:15:33,444 --> 00:15:37,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...as long as our team, the Red Suns, is here.</b></font>

242
00:15:37,544 --> 00:15:40,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're just as proud as I remember.</b></font>

243
00:15:40,114 --> 00:15:42,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But don't forget this...</b></font>

244
00:15:42,454 --> 00:15:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not the same person I was a year ago.</b></font>

245
00:15:49,624 --> 00:15:52,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You beat me last time, but now it's my turn!</b></font>

246
00:15:52,064 --> 00:15:54,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just as you broke my perfect winning record,</b></font>

247
00:15:54,864 --> 00:15:58,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will now break your winning streak!</b></font>

248
00:15:59,704 --> 00:16:02,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry to tell you, but my streak...</b></font>

249
00:16:02,404 --> 00:16:04,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...was broken recently.</b></font>

250
00:16:04,544 --> 00:16:06,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

251
00:16:06,244 --> 00:16:09,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost to an Eight-Six on a
downhill course in Akina.</b></font>

252
00:16:09,574 --> 00:16:10,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you say?!</b></font>

253
00:16:10,914 --> 00:16:12,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was considering retiring,</b></font>

254
00:16:12,914 --> 00:16:15,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I don't want you to
think that I'm running away.</b></font>

255
00:16:15,854 --> 00:16:19,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So maybe I'll agree to a rematch
and race you once more.</b></font>

256
00:16:19,654 --> 00:16:23,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I admire your enthusiasm
in coming all the way here.</b></font>

257
00:16:23,054 --> 00:16:24,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll speak to the other teams</b></font>

258
00:16:24,424 --> 00:16:26,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and arrange for the course in Akagi</b></font>

259
00:16:26,424 --> 00:16:29,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to be free for three days before the race.</b></font>

260
00:16:29,994 --> 00:16:33,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drive as much as you want and get used to it.</b></font>

261
00:16:33,034 --> 00:16:35,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll race you whenever you're ready, Kyoichi.</b></font>

262
00:16:42,914 --> 00:16:46,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a jerk, acting all cool like that!
I'll chase him down and tailgate him!</b></font>

263
00:16:46,914 --> 00:16:50,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't, Seiji. You can't.
You won't be able to catch him.</b></font>

264
00:16:50,284 --> 00:16:52,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't? Such a skinny, frail guy!</b></font>

265
00:16:52,724 --> 00:16:56,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He doesn't look that tough at all.
And that outdated FC...</b></font>

266
00:16:56,524 --> 00:16:59,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He even lost to an Eight-Six, right?</b></font>

267
00:16:59,194 --> 00:17:02,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You idiot! Don't underestimate
Ryosuke Takahashi!</b></font>

268
00:17:02,494 --> 00:17:07,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was solidly defeated by his FC last year!</b></font>

269
00:17:08,904 --> 00:17:10,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The White Comet of Akagi...</i></b></font>

270
00:17:10,974 --> 00:17:15,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I thought I was the only</i>
<i>one who could beat him...</i></b></font>

271
00:17:15,044 --> 00:17:20,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But Ryosuke lost?</i>
<i>He lost to an Eight-Six from Akina?</i></b></font>

272
00:17:22,154 --> 00:17:25,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six has never lost to anyone!</b></font>

273
00:17:25,984 --> 00:17:27,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not to an FC! Not to an FD...</b></font>

274
00:17:27,924 --> 00:17:30,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...not even to an R32!</b></font>

275
00:17:30,354 --> 00:17:36,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I see. That kid was talking</i>
<i>about that same Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

276
00:17:36,534 --> 00:17:38,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder what the driver's like?</i></b></font>

277
00:17:52,014 --> 00:17:53,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Guess who?</b></font>

278
00:17:53,384 --> 00:17:55,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cut it out, Mogi.</b></font>

279
00:17:57,384 --> 00:17:59,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm actually relieved.</b></font>

280
00:17:59,954 --> 00:18:05,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know what I would have done
if you had said some other girl's name.</b></font>

281
00:18:05,364 --> 00:18:07,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Silly...</b></font>

282
00:18:13,504 --> 00:18:16,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi, let's go home.</b></font>

283
00:18:18,874 --> 00:18:21,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, maybe I'll go home alone.</b></font>

284
00:18:21,174 --> 00:18:23,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, I am the lonely driver.</b></font>

285
00:18:23,844 --> 00:18:25,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. So, I should go home alone...</b></font>

286
00:18:25,644 --> 00:18:31,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--The "Eight-Six Power-Up Project."
--What are you talking about?
We have to work today.</b></font>

287
00:18:31,224 --> 00:18:33,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have something to do, too.</b></font>

288
00:18:33,924 --> 00:18:35,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

289
00:18:35,824 --> 00:18:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you, Takumi. Bye!</b></font>

290
00:18:37,394 --> 00:18:39,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bye.</b></font>

291
00:18:39,924 --> 00:18:42,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, Takumi...</b></font>

292
00:18:42,164 --> 00:18:44,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...how far have you two gone since then?</b></font>

293
00:18:44,834 --> 00:18:46,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How far?</b></font>

294
00:18:46,004 --> 00:18:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, come on!</b></font>

295
00:18:47,404 --> 00:18:50,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You and Natsuki! Have you
gone farther than kissing?</b></font>

296
00:18:50,404 --> 00:18:52,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, tell me! Whoops!</b></font>

297
00:19:19,834 --> 00:19:23,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a one-race match.
It'll be decided by a hill climb.</b></font>

298
00:19:23,334 --> 00:19:26,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Fine.
--Shall we begin, then?</b></font>

299
00:19:26,304 --> 00:19:29,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you ready, Seiji?</b></font>

300
00:19:29,044 --> 00:19:31,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anytime!</b></font>

301
00:19:34,014 --> 00:19:36,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't mess this up, Takeshi.</i></b></font>

302
00:19:36,014 --> 00:19:38,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Show them the willpower of Gunma drivers!</i></b></font>

303
00:19:38,884 --> 00:19:41,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just for today, I'll root for you!</i></b></font>

304
00:19:41,894 --> 00:19:44,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Our goal is much more than this race.</i></b></font>

305
00:19:44,694 --> 00:19:47,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Seiji, don't waste time goofing around here.</i></b></font>

306
00:19:47,894 --> 00:19:49,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five seconds to the start!</b></font>

307
00:19:49,934 --> 00:19:52,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four... Three...</b></font>

308
00:19:52,334 --> 00:19:54,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two... One...</b></font>

309
00:19:54,434 --> 00:19:56,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

310
00:20:37,044 --> 00:20:38,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wait and see.</i></b></font>

311
00:20:38,584 --> 00:20:43,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Compared to a Lan-Evo, an R32 is just a toy.</i></b></font>

312
00:20:43,214 --> 00:20:46,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll show you the difference!</b></font>

313
00:20:50,924 --> 00:20:53,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You Emperor punks,</i>
<i>or whatever you call yourselves...</i></b></font>

314
00:20:53,094 --> 00:20:55,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...I will defend Gunma!</i></b></font>

315
00:20:55,834 --> 00:21:00,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And you'll be buried deep</i>
<i>at the bottom of Myogi Valley!</i></b></font>

316
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Whenever I turned around</i></b></font>

317
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was always that</i>
<i>unchanging smile of yours</i></b></font>

318
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It was there on days when</i>
<i>I was too tired to go on</i></b></font>

319
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And even on days with a little happiness in them</i></b></font>

320
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My hands aren't enough</i></b></font>

321
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To hold on to all the love you gave me</i></b></font>

322
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The warm wind</i></b></font>

323
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Comes back quietly and tenderly</i></b></font>

324
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And as I gaze at the sky alone</i></b></font>

325
00:22:23,554 --> 00:22:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You smile down upon me</i></b></font>

326
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are still waving to me from the radiant light</i></b></font>

327
00:22:38,704 --> 00:22:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just like you did that day</i></b></font>

328
00:22:51,384 --> 00:22:57,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are my everlasting memory</i></b></font>

329
00:23:04,394 --> 00:23:07,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I don't stop them, who will?!</i></b></font>

330
00:23:07,894 --> 00:23:10,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: Second Stage...</i></b></font>

331
00:23:10,364 --> 00:23:12,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Team Emperor on Akina!"</i></b></font>

332
00:23:12,434 --> 00:23:15,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Anyone who doesn't watch this is beneath me!</i></b></font>

